Package: mmorpg-monolith
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, docker-compose-plugin | docker-compose
Maintainer: Samuel <lordnns@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Lordnns/MMORPG
Description: MMORPG lab — all-in-one deployment
 Single-host deployment of the MMORPG architecture lab: redis,
 orchestrator, gatekeeper, and locally-spawned DS containers all
 managed by docker compose on one VM.
 .
 Configure /etc/default/mmorpg-monolith, then:
   systemctl start mmorpg-monolith
